p8-platform
------------------------------------------
This library provides platform specific support for other libraries, and is
used by libCEC and binary add-ons for Kodi.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libgcc1-14.4.0-1
  libp8-platform-devel-2.1.0.1-1bl2
  libp8-platform2-2.1.0.1-1bl2
  libstdc++6-14.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/Pulse-Eight/platform

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/Pulse-Eight/platform.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack p8-platform-2.1.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./p8-platform-2.1.0.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/p8-platform-2.1.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/p8-platform-2.1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libp8-platform2-2.1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libp8-platform-devel-2.1.0.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(p8-platform)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/p8-platform.README
  /usr/share/doc/p8-platform/README.md

(libp8-platform2)
  /usr/bin/cygp8-platform-2.dll

(libp8-platform-devel)
  /usr/include/p8-platform/os.h
  /usr/include/p8-platform/posix/os-socket.h
  /usr/include/p8-platform/posix/os-threads.h
  /usr/include/p8-platform/posix/os-types.h
  /usr/include/p8-platform/sockets/cdevsocket.h
  /usr/include/p8-platform/sockets/socket.h
  /usr/include/p8-platform/sockets/tcp.h
  /usr/include/p8-platform/threads/atomics.h
  /usr/include/p8-platform/threads/mutex.h
  /usr/include/p8-platform/threads/threads.h
  /usr/include/p8-platform/util/StdString.h
  /usr/include/p8-platform/util/StringUtils.h
  /usr/include/p8-platform/util/atomic.h
  /usr/include/p8-platform/util/buffer.h
  /usr/include/p8-platform/util/timeutils.h
  /usr/include/p8-platform/util/util.h
  /usr/lib/cmake/p8-platform/p8-platform-config.cmake
  /usr/lib/libp8-platform.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/p8-platform.pc

